&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Resourcing Technical Lead&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;NHS Jobs, On-Boarding, Line Manager Portal and ESR provide electronic methods of advertising, recruiting and managing candidates who are new to the Trust, or have moved internally. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;They provide a means for individuals and managers to complete the necessary recruitment and employment information. The aim of these systems is to improve the employee journey, reduce time to hire, support the individual and manager, and ensuring a seamless process for their new hire.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As &lt;span&gt;the Technical Lead for the Resourcing department, you will provide high level technical support, ensuring that our recruitment systems are efficient and effective in the recruitment of the Trust’s diverse workforce, alongside our business needs.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;You will use your proven analytic skills to provide leadership, guidance and convey complex technical issues to a wide range of audiences. This support will include playing a vital role in the on-going development and maintenance of the systems, including auditing data integrity and data quality assurance.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;This is a professional role located within the LTHT Resourcing team of the HR and OD Directorate working closely with all other members of the HR Service, managers and staff. You will also have the opportunity to contribute to and lead on specific HR projects and activities.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;For more information on this role please contact Lindsay Godfrey on 0113 2066132 or email lindsay.godfrey@nhs.net.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
